        "Description": "Good Day 47,\rGuess who’s back? Back again. Sharty’s back—and he brings this contract to Berlin.\r\rInstead of staying in the spotlight, our target lingers outside the club, away from the chaos but still stirring trouble.\rFind him outside, make it loud, make it clear, and end the show before the crowd even knows what happened.\r\rGood Luck.\r\rBy - SW\r\n\r\n<HCCE>",
